Audio::Ardour::Irc version 0.1
==================================

Audio::Ardour::Irc passes OSC messages to Ardour allowing control
by (for example) an infra red remote.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Net::LibLO
  File::HomeDir

